// Deduplicates the append-only PRODAFTUstaCompromisedCards_CL table so that each
// USTA ticket (TicketId) appears exactly once. Log Analytics is append-only and has no
// unique-key/upsert, so the same TicketId can be ingested more than once (backfill/poller
// overlap, or a ticket whose status changes and is re-fetched). This parser keeps the most
// recently ingested copy of each ticket, so consumers always see one row per ticket with
// its latest status. Query this function instead of the raw *_CL table.
PRODAFTUstaCompromisedCards_CL
| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by TicketId

